WEBVTT

1
00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:54.950
Guess I'll head to work.

2
00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:20.490
I can make 60,000 a month cutting trees.

3
00:01:20.980 --> 00:01:25.740
For the kidney, I got 1,200,000.

4
00:01:26.310 --> 00:01:29.490
For my right eye, 300,000.

5
00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:32.750
And for one of my balls...

6
00:01:33.150 --> 00:01:35.150
How much did I get for it, again?

7
00:01:35.150 --> 00:01:37.330
I don't think it was even 100,000.

8
00:01:40.390 --> 00:01:42.880
And I'm still in debt...

9
00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:45.880
to the tune of 38,040,000.

10
00:01:50.010 --> 00:01:53.190
I know, Pochita.

11
00:01:53.190 --> 00:01:55.270
Let's go kill one.

12
00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:00.740
I can make around 300,000 from killing just one devil.

13
00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:07.740
Yup, nothing beats being a devil hunter.

14
00:02:22.670 --> 00:02:25.260
This is a tomato devil.

15
00:02:25.720 --> 00:02:28.820
It can come back from its seeds, 
so you should burn it.

16
00:02:28.820 --> 00:02:31.010
Good work, Denji.

17
00:02:31.380 --> 00:02:35.540
This one's corpse will fetch a hefty sum on the black market.

18
00:02:35.540 --> 00:02:37.520
I'll give you 400,000.

19
00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.420
Thanks!

20
00:02:38.420 --> 00:02:41.670
Minus your loan repayments and interest, that's 170,000.

21
00:02:41.670 --> 00:02:49.150
Then after accounting for the brokerage fee, 
admin fee, overheads, and so on...

22
00:02:49.910 --> 00:02:51.650
I'm left with 70,000.

23
00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:58.920
And after paying the water bill and some of my other debts...

24
00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:00.910
Would you look at that?

25
00:03:01.610 --> 00:03:04.410
Only 1,800 yen left.

26
00:03:04.970 --> 00:03:10.650
There's no food at home, 
and we've gotta survive the month on this.

27
00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:15.260
Pochita, today's meal is one slice of bread.

28
00:03:21.590 --> 00:03:25.060
Why d'ya keep a brat like that 
'round as a devil hunter?

29
00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:29.250
He's repaying his debt to us.

30
00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:32.940
Well, really it's the debt his piece-of-shit father left when he died.

31
00:03:33.350 --> 00:03:37.320
But how can a kid who's got a devil for a pet really be a devil hunter, y'know?

32
00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:40.590
Put it this way, a real devil hunter

33
00:03:40.590 --> 00:03:44.830
would never sell the corpses to yakuza like us.

34
00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:49.330
The good thing about Denji is that he's obedient.

35
00:03:54.670 --> 00:03:56.300
Yo, pooch!

36
00:03:57.440 --> 00:03:59.980
I'll give ya 100 yen to eat this smoke.

37
00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.220
Really?!

38
00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:05.790
Don't mind if I do!

39
00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:14.420
I'll call you when another devil shows up.

40
00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:16.860
And if you try to run, I'll feed you to the pigs.

41
00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:35.070
We've got enough for three days' food.

42
00:04:38.300 --> 00:04:40.510
I heard something the other day.

43
00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:44.520
People normally put jam on their bread.

44
00:04:45.050 --> 00:04:48.690
Well, being normal would be a dream come true.

45
00:04:49.450 --> 00:04:52.780
Don't think I'll pay off all this debt before I die.

46
00:04:56.490 --> 00:05:00.290
And I'll probably never have a girlfriend.

47
00:05:00.700 --> 00:05:04.020
Can't bring a girl back to a shack like this.

48
00:05:04.020 --> 00:05:05.910
Got no money to take her out on a date, either.

49
00:05:10.950 --> 00:05:13.180
If I could have just one dream come true,

50
00:05:13.180 --> 00:05:15.760
it'd be to sleep with a woman before I die.

51
00:05:31.380 --> 00:05:35.460
Went and hung himself without even making this month's repayment.

52
00:05:36.220 --> 00:05:39.710
Kid, I don't care if you have to beg or sell your body.

53
00:05:39.710 --> 00:05:42.410
Get me 700,000 yen by tomorrow.

54
00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:46.490
Otherwise I'll chop up your corpse and sell the pieces.

55
00:06:01.050 --> 00:06:02.420
A-A chainsaw?!

56
00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:08.610
It's a devil.

57
00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.350
If you want to kill me, go ahead.

58
00:06:12.810 --> 00:06:14.060
I'm dead anyway.

59
00:06:22.940 --> 00:06:24.120
It's hurt.

60
00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:27.620
Are you gonna die too?

61
00:06:34.070 --> 00:06:35.050
Bite me!

62
00:06:35.430 --> 00:06:38.930
I've heard that devils can heal by drinking blood.

63
00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:41.090
Bite me if you wanna live!

64
00:06:53.820 --> 00:06:56.280
My blood ain't free, though.

65
00:06:56.280 --> 00:06:57.950
This is a contract.

66
00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:00.190
I'm saving your life,

67
00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.200
so you gotta save mine.

68
00:07:05.190 --> 00:07:08.380
I wanna live too, after all.

69
00:07:21.740 --> 00:07:25.740
Would you hire me as a devil hunter?

70
00:07:33.350 --> 00:07:35.480
Too hungry to fall asleep.

71
00:07:35.990 --> 00:07:39.940
And lying here, all I can think about is my debt, 
which makes it even harder to fall asleep.

72
00:07:42.740 --> 00:07:45.860
I know what I want to dream of tonight.

73
00:07:46.410 --> 00:07:48.360
I'm gonna put jam on bread,

74
00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:50.090
eat it together with you,

75
00:07:50.090 --> 00:07:52.610
fool around with a girl,

76
00:07:52.610 --> 00:07:56.240
play video games with her, 
and fall asleep holding her in my arms.

77
00:07:57.660 --> 00:07:58.500
Sounds good, right?

78
00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:20.050
I heard that my mom died from some heart illness that made her cough up blood.

79
00:08:23.310 --> 00:08:26.940
Denji, we have a devil. Time for work.

80
00:08:45.470 --> 00:08:49.430
At least let me have my night-time dream.

81
00:09:15.370 --> 00:09:17.740
A devil showed up in a place like this?

82
00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.250
I don't see it.

83
00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:27.010
Is it hiding?

84
00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:31.020
Maybe it's gone already.

85
00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:44.060
Denji.

86
00:09:44.060 --> 00:09:47.530
We're grateful to you, you know.

87
00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:49.670
Huh? Okay.

88
00:09:49.670 --> 00:09:51.790
You're obedient like a dog.

89
00:09:52.140 --> 00:09:55.840
And you work for scraps like a dog.

90
00:09:57.990 --> 00:10:00.920
But I hate the stench of dogs.

91
00:10:13.790 --> 00:10:16.440
You see, as yakuza,

92
00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:20.430
we want to become stronger so that we can make more money.

93
00:10:20.740 --> 00:10:24.750
So we decided to make a contract with a devil, like you did.

94
00:10:27.430 --> 00:10:31.330
We want the power that they can provide.

95
00:10:31.670 --> 00:10:36.830
And what I want is the death of all devil hunters!

96
00:10:38.380 --> 00:10:40.630
Little devil hunter.

97
00:10:40.630 --> 00:10:43.130
These guys are real stupid.

98
00:10:43.130 --> 00:10:44.210
Absolute idiots.

99
00:10:44.730 --> 00:10:51.220
Just the promise of devil powers was enough for them to willingly become my slaves.

100
00:10:51.490 --> 00:10:54.650
Little did they know that power would turn them into zombies.

101
00:10:54.650 --> 00:10:57.230
Because I'm a zombie devil.

102
00:10:58.280 --> 00:11:01.980
And I hate devil hunters, because they kill us devils.

103
00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:04.490
So I kill them.

104
00:11:06.170 --> 00:11:11.490
Guys, tear him apart, and then throw the pieces in the trash or something.

105
00:11:12.230 --> 00:11:13.230
Shit!

106
00:11:29.080 --> 00:11:30.130
The exit...

107
00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:48.100
Let go!

108
00:12:00.560 --> 00:12:04.000
It's not like I wanted to be rich.

109
00:12:04.630 --> 00:12:08.210
I just wanted a normal life.

110
00:12:09.630 --> 00:12:12.680
But I couldn't even have that!

111
00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:54.090
Pochita!

112
00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:55.630
Pochita!

113
00:12:56.740 --> 00:12:59.260
Pochita, we have work to do.

114
00:13:11.950 --> 00:13:16.940
Pochita, I might die while fighting devils.

115
00:13:17.780 --> 00:13:21.160
If that happens, leaving you on your own would be my only regret.

116
00:13:21.610 --> 00:13:24.170
Are you going to starve to death?

117
00:13:24.650 --> 00:13:27.920
Are you going to be killed by another devil hunter?

118
00:13:32.180 --> 00:13:36.300
I've heard that some devils can take over the bodies of dead humans.

119
00:13:37.070 --> 00:13:39.550
If you can do that,

120
00:13:40.160 --> 00:13:42.620
I want you to have my body.

121
00:13:44.180 --> 00:13:48.060
When I die, the yakuza will finally stop coming after me.

122
00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:51.570
Then you can leave this town.

123
00:13:51.930 --> 00:13:53.100
And then...

124
00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:55.070
Yeah.

125
00:13:55.790 --> 00:14:00.330
You can live a normal life, and die like a normal person.

126
00:14:04.170 --> 00:14:06.220
Make my dream come true.

127
00:14:34.280 --> 00:14:35.280
Pochita?!

128
00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:41.030
Did you manage to take over my body?

129
00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:47.780
I've loved listening to you talk about your dreams.

130
00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:52.120
This is a contract.

131
00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:53.920
I'll give you my heart.

132
00:14:54.390 --> 00:14:58.800
In exchange, let me see your dreams come true.

133
00:14:59.080 --> 00:14:59.670
Pochita!

134
00:15:06.620 --> 00:15:07.710
I'm not hurt?!

135
00:15:14.700 --> 00:15:15.810
Pochita...

136
00:15:23.710 --> 00:15:25.080
Huh? What's going on?

137
00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:27.810
You're alive after being torn to pieces?

138
00:15:27.810 --> 00:15:29.580
How come? Gross!

139
00:15:29.830 --> 00:15:32.580
This is why I hate devil hunters.

140
00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:36.000
Guys, eat him!

141
00:15:41.870 --> 00:15:44.790
Why did these guys go looking for an even better life

142
00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:47.100
when they already had it so good?

143
00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:49.600
Maybe I'm no different.

144
00:15:50.320 --> 00:15:53.600
The happiness I had from having Pochita with me wasn't enough.

145
00:15:54.040 --> 00:15:57.360
I still dreamed of a better life.

146
00:15:58.180 --> 00:16:01.610
Right. Everyone has their dreams.

147
00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:04.740
Then I suppose it's not a bad thing.

148
00:16:05.970 --> 00:16:08.370
It's not a bad thing,

149
00:16:10.180 --> 00:16:13.380
but if you interfere with mine,

150
00:16:15.770 --> 00:16:17.130
you can fuckin' die!

151
00:16:25.910 --> 00:16:28.890
No way he'd survive being eaten.

152
00:17:01.280 --> 00:17:02.800
What the hell?!

153
00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:06.800
Did that puny devil take over his body?

154
00:17:07.600 --> 00:17:09.060
Are you on our side now?

155
00:17:30.050 --> 00:17:32.040
Ouch.

156
00:17:44.810 --> 00:17:46.640
No! That hurts!

157
00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:50.890
Stay away!

158
00:17:55.050 --> 00:17:56.430
Get fucked!

159
00:17:56.430 --> 00:17:59.430
Stay away! Stay away! Stay away!

160
00:17:59.430 --> 00:18:01.940
Stay away! Stay away!

161
00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:03.940
Don't come near me!

162
00:18:17.710 --> 00:18:19.460
Die!

163
00:18:55.970 --> 00:19:01.540
Looks like you lot have become devils to the core.

164
00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:05.300
Since you did pay me to be a devil hunter,

165
00:19:05.300 --> 00:19:09.550
I'd better do my job and kill you all, then!

166
00:19:15.150 --> 00:19:16.090
Oh, yeah!

167
00:19:16.090 --> 00:19:19.470
If I kill every last one of you,

168
00:19:19.470 --> 00:19:21.230
then I can wave goodbye to my debt too!

169
00:20:08.460 --> 00:20:10.440
Someone beat us to it.

170
00:20:19.450 --> 00:20:21.050
There's one still alive.

171
00:20:34.470 --> 00:20:35.930
Oh?

172
00:20:36.410 --> 00:20:39.680
You smell interesting.

173
00:20:40.120 --> 00:20:42.940
Neither like a human, nor like a demon.

174
00:20:45.450 --> 00:20:47.680
Is this your handiwork?

175
00:20:50.910 --> 00:20:54.110
H-Hold me...

176
00:21:13.560 --> 00:21:14.670
He's human.

177
00:21:15.190 --> 00:21:17.420
Could he be possessed by a devil?

178
00:21:17.900 --> 00:21:19.270
No.

179
00:21:19.270 --> 00:21:21.440
I would be able to tell from his face.

180
00:21:24.060 --> 00:21:27.170
I came here to kill the zombie devil.

181
00:21:27.170 --> 00:21:29.690
I'm a devil hunter from the Public Safety Bureau.

182
00:21:33.810 --> 00:21:36.080
You have a choice.

183
00:21:37.030 --> 00:21:40.200
You can be a devil that I kill.

184
00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:43.370
Or you can be my human pet.

185
00:21:44.250 --> 00:21:47.200
Know that I feed my pets properly.

186
00:21:56.180 --> 00:21:57.660
You'd feed me?

187
00:21:58.770 --> 00:22:00.720
What would I get for breakfast?

188
00:22:01.190 --> 00:22:02.270
Hmm...

189
00:22:03.050 --> 00:22:08.190
Bread with butter and jam, salad, coffee,

190
00:22:08.190 --> 00:22:12.230
and then maybe something for dessert, I guess.

191
00:22:13.850 --> 00:22:14.740
What?

192
00:22:20.760 --> 00:22:23.720
That sounds awesome.
